OL,6,F"They have the curriculum there at the
OL,7,Fschools where they cover wellbeing and
OL,8,Fhealth and safety and all these sorts
OL,9,Fof things. And sometimes it's helpful
OL,10,Fto have a bit of police expertise on
OL,11,Fthat. So one of the most common inputs
OL,12,FI do is internet safety.
OL,14,F"But I can also cover road safety,
OL,15,Fdrugs awareness mainly around the
OL,16,Flegislation.
