OL,6,F"I've had incidents where children
OL,7,Fhave come and disclosed stuff to me
OL,8,Ffollowing an input or, not long kind
OL,9,Fof after an input, which just to me is
OL,10,Fsuccess, as you say, is quite hard to
OL,11,Fquantify.
OL,13,F"Like how can you measure what you
OL,14,Fprevent rather than what you've
OL,15,Fthey've dealt with? But yeah, I've
OL,16,Fdealt with a few incidents of online
OL,17,Fbullying, online child exploitation.
