OL,6,F"There's an incident which I probably
OL,7,Fcan't speak about the full details of,
OL,8,Fbut where a child was being groomed
OL,9,Fonline. And then they've come to me,
OL,10,Fthey've disclosed that, and we've been
OL,11,Fable to send that away to the relevant
OL,12,Fforce, whether that was originating
OL,13,Ffrom."
OL,15,FScottish Borders teacher Vix Shannon
OL,16,Fbelieves that having a police officer
OL,17,Fin and around the school is only a
OL,18,Fgood thing and something that wasn't
OL,19,Favailable to her throughout her school
OL,20,Fyears.
