OL,6,FShe said: "When I was at school, we
OL,7,Fdidn't have that connection with the,
OL,8,Fthe police.
OL,10,F"They were sort of like they were sort
OL,11,Fof set aside and sort of, you know,
OL,12,Fthey were inaccessible to children,
OL,13,Freally.
OL,15,F"And you always had a bit of fear,
OL,16,Fwhereas I think, PC Luke Cameron comes
OL,17,Fin and he comes to events in the
OL,18,Fschool. He is just another one of
OL,19,Fthose adults that you can talk to."
